  /************************************************
  ddcurl library
  by Dody Rachmat Wicaksono (dodyrw@gmail.com)

  version 1.0
  Nov 26 2010
  ************************************************/
  
  ddcurl is a set of php functions to simplify CURL command.
  In most case, we use curl to fetch data from the website.
  Sometimes this process need us to POST form data, login and
  maintain web session. ddcurl offer a wrapper of a series of 
  CURL command to make it easy and fun!
  
  Thank you for using ddcurl!